{"tid":1320242,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"721唔好太輕敵啊各位","createTime":"2019-07-15T10:47:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T08:27:53.000Z","uid":21832,"like":63,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"113d26ca9cfc448132b74c2bbd80856afe42664e","tid":1320242,"uid":21832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:47:17.000Z","msg":"721唔好太輕敵啊各位<br />\n<br />\n睇嗰幾隻狗俾人圍係大快人心，但唔好忘記嗰幾隻狗係輕裝落單嘅老狗先俾你圍到咋，而且我哋受傷嘅人比佢哋多好多<br />\n721面對嘅係全武裝幾十個一隊計嘅大部隊，到時班狗一定發晒矛要報仇<br />\n<br />\n我哋仲係啱啱離開新手村好低LV㗎咋，唔好太得意忘形啊"},{"pid":"a1a314c775a657aaf2f79c1ff7f9c46f0b3cc39c","tid":1320242,"uid":210612,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:48:09.000Z","msg":"狗方急不及待想試水砲車既厲害"},{"pid":"46bc7e3a646f69015a3765a2db5280cc253e8865","tid":1320242,"uid":276964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T15:05:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8c9d3ea4c937f47fc6b6274031e4229c1283166b","tid":1320242,"uid":82432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T15:09:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1609d8cbda27847e8c308dc8593105367ec993f6","tid":1320242,"uid":12824,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T15:10:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fab040d8fbd4c2157c42a18b2f5070a01eea63f7","tid":1320242,"uid":70888,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T15:14:29.000Z","msg":"岩，佢地實會報復<br />\n先唔講點樣打，講左點樣保護手足唔好落單先<br />\n721邊面落單都比人打到仆街"},{"pid":"1af32620dc221f87d536871cf76a40016d1fd1e6","tid":1320242,"uid":162272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T15:17:27.000Z","msg":"想嚇走哂啲和理非？"},{"pid":"5ee877e7270de29d8a25e2f77294ccd4d45017f0","tid":1320242,"uid":142965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T16:45:42.000Z","msg":"[經典重溫] 日本學生擊敗防暴警察<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dhMxiT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dhMxiT</a>"},{"pid":"b3f194d442e13cbb64731b6dc6b5a0c95b0caa01","tid":1320242,"